BLG Capital, a real estate
investment manager run by Turkish businessman Serdar Bilgili,
said it raised 142.4 million euros ($187 million) for a fund to
invest in projects in  Turkey .  The BLG Turkish Real Estate Fund LP, whose global placement
agent is London-based MVision Private Equity Advisers Ltd., will
use the money for a student accommodation facility in Istanbul
and to develop a former warehouse in the cityâ€™s Maslak business
